\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Multi-agent pipeline. Agent~1 (Intent Classifier) detects language and domain, routing the input to the correct dataset and model. Agent~2 (Classification Agent) runs one of eight classifiers (seven classical data mining models or a transformer) and returns the predicted label with confidence scores. Agent~3 (XAI Agent) generates explanations using \texttt  {shap.Explainer} (generic, model-agnostic) and \texttt  {LimeTextExplainer}, both applied uniformly across all model types.}}{5}{figure.caption.4}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:architecture}{{1}{5}{Multi-agent pipeline. Agent~1 (Intent Classifier) detects language and domain, routing the input to the correct dataset and model. Agent~2 (Classification Agent) runs one of eight classifiers (seven classical data mining models or a transformer) and returns the predicted label with confidence scores. Agent~3 (XAI Agent) generates explanations using \texttt {shap.Explainer} (generic, model-agnostic) and \texttt {LimeTextExplainer}, both applied uniformly across all model types}{figure.caption.4}{}}
